ActPublic Service Employment Act
SubjectTransfer of a Portion of the Canadian Food Inspection Agency Regulations
PrecisTRANSFER OF A PORTION OF THE CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY REGULATIONS in order to apply subsection 132(1) of the Public Service Employment Act to all persons employed or engaged in the portion of the federal public administration in the Canadian Food Inspection Agency known as the Domestic Terrestrial Animal Pathogen Unit.
